         If I wanted to be a wizard I would have made one.  </P><P>That being said I do think the necro is a viable class RIGHT NOW - that doesn't mean that there are not balance issues to consider.  Clerics are a viable class right now and they are getting worked over.  Why did this turn into a pissing match about who does more damage?</P><P>But ok I'll bite... what is it that would make us the masters of damage over a long battle like that?</P><P>How about this:</P><P>A dot that checked the mobs HPS like dragon bane or giants bane - if the mob has more than 100k hps than the dot does 15k over 4 minutes.</P><P>Funeral pyre assuming perfect casting would do 8k over that amount of time...</P><P>Of course it could always be argued that a wizard could always nuke for more blah blah blah...</P><P>BUT if we had a new line of dots that were like this - added to the dots that already land - this should and would push us over the edge on LONG term damage - and that's what everyone wants right?</P><P>Making the check for 100k hps would keep the dots from being used to kite gore around DL... not that verant seems to care about the old dragons anymore....</P><P></P><P>- CK<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
